# Validation Checklist

Use on every structure update:

**Process**

- [ ] Interview completed and user confirmed
- [ ] Impact assessed per [structure.md — Flows](../consultation/structure.md#flows)
- [ ] Templates applied for new files
- [ ] Cross-references validated
- [ ] Open questions captured; summary with changed files presented

**IDs and traceability**

- [ ] `F##` consistent (filename, frontmatter, features-list, backlog, traceability)
- [ ] `UR-F##-##`, `FR-F##-##`, `NFR-##`, `ADR-##` consistent
- [ ] `features-list` derived from `GOL-##` / `SCN-##` per [02-features-list.mdc](02-features-list.mdc); brief ↔ UR summaries; **Requires** ↔ diagram ↔ frontmatter
- [ ] Feature **Status** consistent; transitions per [03-feature-lifecycle.mdc](03-feature-lifecycle.mdc)
- [ ] **In development** only if all **Requires** are **Implemented**
- [ ] **Implemented** only if all linked `BL-##` are `Done`
- [ ] Traceability chain per [06-traceability.mdc](06-traceability.mdc)
- [ ] Glossary terms linked on first use per file

**Architecture**

- [ ] Solution strategy ready per [04-solution-strategy.mdc](04-solution-strategy.mdc) before BB/RT/db-and-dfd edits
- [ ] No open `Q-A##` when architecture downstream docs are updated
- [ ] `NFR-##` / `ADR-##` consistent; bidirectional links to features per [06-traceability.mdc](06-traceability.mdc)
- [ ] Blocks have Level, Parent, Type; containment matches diagrams
- [ ] Runtime participants map to `building-blocks.md` or documented external
- [ ] Scenarios have trigger, interactions, notable aspects; errors when significant
- [ ] Mermaid updated where flows changed

**Mockups** *(when present)*

- [ ] Every linked `MCK-##` resolves to SVG or explicit spec-only (`—`)
- [ ] No orphan SVGs; filename prefix matches ID
- [ ] SVG well-formed XML; paths relative to `4-design/`
- [ ] Journey **Visual flow** uses existing `MCK-##` / `JRN-##`

**Deliverables**

- [ ] `6-code/` traceability updated if adopted and upstream changed materially

