# Open Questions

One file at product root: `open-questions.md`. Template: [templates.md — open-questions.md](../consultation/templates.md#open-questionsmd).

| Section | ID prefix | Phase area |
|---------|-----------|------------|
| Scope | `Q-S##` | `1-scope/` |
| Features | `Q-F##-##` | `2-features/` — include **Feature** column |
| Architecture | `Q-A##` | `3-arch/` |
| Design | `Q-D##` | `4-design/` |
| Development | `Q-V##` | `5-dev/`, `6-code/` |

**Rules:** one row per question; **open only** — remove when answered; record answer in the target doc, not here. Prefix `<a id="q-…"></a>` on the `#` cell (slug = lowercase ID, e.g. `Q-V01` → `#q-v01`). Do not duplicate questions in phase or feature files.
